c
 P(x) = b_0 + b_1 x + b_2 x^2 + \cdots b_n x^n
P(x) = a_0  + a_1 (x - c) + a_2 ( x- c)^2 + a_3(x - c)^3\cdots a_n(x - c)^n
a_0  = P(c)
x^r=(x-c+c)^r
=\sum_{0\le t\le r}\binom rt (x-c)^{r-t}c^t=(x-c)^r+\binom r1 (x-c)^{r-1}c+ \binom r2 (x-c)^{r-2}c^2+\cdots+\binom r{r-2} (x-c)^{2}c^{r-2}+\binom r{r-1} (x-c)^1c^{r-1}+c^r
r=0,1,2,3,\cdots,n-1,n
\binom nr=0
r>n
r<0
Q(x) = P(x + c)
Q(x - c) = P(x)
